---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="FAQ - ReguMe" 
  description="Frequently asked questions about ReguMe health protocol organizer."
>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      Find answers to common questions about ReguMe below. Can't find what you're looking for? 
      <a href="/contact">Contact us</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>General Questions</h2>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">What is ReguMe?</h3>
      <p>
        ReguMe is a mobile app that extracts health and wellness protocols from social media 
        videos (TikTok, Instagram, YouTube) and helps you organize and track them. It transforms 
        scattered wellness advice into actionable daily routines.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Is ReguMe free?</h3>
      <p>
        ReguMe offers a free tier with basic features. Premium features may be available through 
        in-app purchases or subscriptions. Check the app for current pricing.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">What platforms are supported?</h3>
      <p>
        ReguMe currently extracts protocols from:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>TikTok</li>
        <li>Instagram (posts and reels)</li>
        <li>YouTube</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Is my data private?</h3>
      <p>
        Yes. Your health data is encrypted and secure. We never sell your personal information. 
        Read our <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a> for full details.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2>Medical & Safety</h2>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Is ReguMe medical advice?</h3>
      <div class="alert alert-warning">
        <p>
          <strong>NO.</strong> ReguMe provides informational content only and is not a substitute 
          for professional medical advice. Always consult healthcare professionals before following 
          any health protocols.
        </p>
      </div>
      <p>
        See our <a href="/medical-disclaimer">Medical Disclaimer</a> for important details.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Are protocols verified by doctors?</h3>
      <p>
        <strong>No.</strong> Protocols are extracted from social media content created by various 
        content creators who may not be medical professionals. We do not verify medical accuracy, 
        safety, or efficacy.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Always verify information with your healthcare provider before following any protocol.</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Can I use ReguMe to treat medical conditions?</h3>
      <p>
        <strong>No.</strong> ReguMe is not a medical tool and should not be used to diagnose, 
        treat, or manage medical conditions. Consult healthcare professionals for medical treatment.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2>App Features</h2>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">How do I import a protocol?</h3>
      <ol>
        <li>Open ReguMe app</li>
        <li>Tap the "+" button or "Import" tab</li>
        <li>Paste a video URL from TikTok, Instagram, or YouTube</li>
        <li>Wait for AI to extract the protocol</li>
        <li>Review and save to your library</li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">How do I track my progress?</h3>
      <p>
        ReguMe provides daily action checklists for each protocol. Simply check off items as 
        you complete them. Progress is automatically tracked and visualized in the app.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Can I create custom protocols?</h3>
      <p>
        Yes! You can create custom protocols by manually entering supplements, habits, and 
        routines directly in the app.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">How do I delete my account?</h3>
      <p>
        You can delete your account and all associated data at any time:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>In-app:</strong> Go to Settings → Account → Delete Account</li>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> Contact <a href="mailto:privacy@regume.com">privacy@regume.com</a></li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        See our <a href="/data-deletion">Data Deletion page</a> for full details.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2>Technical</h2>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">What devices are supported?</h3>
      <p>
        ReguMe requires:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>iOS:</strong> Version 14.0 or later</li>
        <li><strong>iPhone:</strong> iPhone 7 or newer recommended</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Why isn't my video importing?</h3>
      <p>Possible reasons:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Video is private or age-restricted</li>
        <li>Video was deleted by creator</li>
        <li>URL format is incorrect</li>
        <li>Platform API is temporarily unavailable</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Try copying the URL again or contact <a href="mailto:support@regume.com">support@regume.com</a> 
        for help.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">How do I report a bug?</h3>
      <p>
        Email us at <a href="mailto:support@regume.com">support@regume.com</a> with:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Description of the bug</li>
        <li>Steps to reproduce</li>
        <li>Your device model and iOS version</li>
        <li>Screenshots (if applicable)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h2>Privacy & Legal</h2>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">What data do you collect?</h3>
      <p>
        We collect email, account information, saved protocols, tracking data, and usage analytics. 
        See our <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a> for complete details.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">How do I delete my data?</h3>
      <p>
        See our <a href="/data-deletion">Data Deletion page</a> for instructions on deleting 
        your account and data.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Do you sell my data?</h3>
      <p>
        <strong>No.</strong> We never sell user data. We may share anonymized, aggregated data 
        for research purposes, but this cannot be linked back to you.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2>Content & Copyright</h2>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Who owns the protocols?</h3>
      <p>
        Original content creators own their content. ReguMe provides attribution and links to 
        sources. We extract text-based protocols for organizational purposes under fair use.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">How do I report copyright infringement?</h3>
      <p>
        See our <a href="/dmca-policy">DMCA Policy</a> for instructions on filing a copyright claim.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Can I share protocols with others?</h3>
      <p>
        Yes! You can share protocols within the app. Attribution to original creators is maintained 
        in all shared content.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="alert alert-info" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Still have questions?</h3>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
        <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@regume.com">support@regume.com</a><br/>
        <strong>Response time:</strong> Within 48 hours (business days)
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

